=24&d=retro", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/618b11cc34d4d0f927d137a11b4bf784?s=48&d=retro", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/618b11cc34d4d0f927d137a11b4bf784?s=73&d=retro", "created": 1495073455, "last_modified": 1766130912, "pro": 0}, "last_reply_by": "flavoury", "last_touched": 1775455854, "title": "职场汇报发言总是紧张、语无伦次，自信不够怎么办", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1203735", "created": 1775406277, "deleted": 0, "content": "1 、我其实是一个公认比较有头脑、逻辑清晰的人。私下场合我经常是主要的观点输出者。\r\n2 、但是工作会议场合总是表现不佳，特别是向上汇报的场合，会因为紧张而忘了本来该说的话，忘词，语无伦次，给人的感觉不自信，本来自己做的是 90 分，很可能被我说成只有 60 分。\r\n3 、目前看已经成了我职业发展的主要短板了，我工作业绩很不错，但是汇报能力真的不大行。如果能解决这个，估计能更上一层楼\r\n4 、怎样能做系统性的提升？求 V 友指教。包括书籍、课程等", "content_rendered": "1 、我其实是一个公认比较有头脑、逻辑清晰的人。私下场合我经常是主要的观点输出者。<br />2 、但是工作会议场合总是表现不佳，特别是向上汇报的场合，会因为紧张而忘了本来该说的话，忘词，语无伦次，给人的感觉不自信，本来自己做的是 90 分，很可能被我说成只有 60 分。<br />3 、目前看已经成了我职业发展的主要短板了，我工作业绩很不错，但是汇报能力真的不大行。如果能解决这个，估计能更上一层楼<br />4 、怎样能做系统性的提升？求 V 友指教。包括书籍、课程等", "last_modified": 1775409165, "replies": 25, "id": 1203735}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c74d/97b0/16_large.png?m=1727584731", "name": "share", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c74d/97b0/16_normal.png?m=1727584731", "title": "分享发现", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/share", "topics": 45852, "footer": "", "header": "分享你看到的好玩的，有信息量的，欢迎从这里获取灵感。", "title_alternative": "Share", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c74d/97b0/16_mini.png?m=1727584731", "stars": 6267, "founder_id": 0, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 16, "parent_node_name": "v2ex"}, "member": {"id": 4627, "username": "thinkever", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/thinkever", "website": "", "twitter": "", "psn": "", "github": "", "btc": "", "location": "", "tagline": "", "bio": "", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/0d1a/9651/4627_mini.png?m=1754710687", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/0d1a/9651/4627_normal.png?m=1754710687", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/0d1a/9651/4627_large.png?m=1754710687", "avatar_xlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/0d1a/9651/4627_xlarge.png?m=1754710687", "avatar_xxlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/0d1a/9651/4627_xxlarge.png?m=1754710687", "avatar_xxxlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/0d1a/9651/4627_xxxlarge.png?m=1754710687", "created": 1294039870, "last_modified": 1754710687, "pro": 0}, "last_reply_by": "zpzpzp", "last_touched": 1775456448, "title": "士别三日刮目相看，全系切换为 edge 浏览器", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1203752", "created": 1775432986, "deleted": 0, "content": "之前的话主力浏览器一直是 pc 和 mac 端 chrome ，安卓端 Firefox nightly ，ios 端 Safari 。\r\n\r\n之前 edge 用过一段时间又屁滚尿流切换回来了，很多地方的小 bug 不舒服。\r\n\r\n但这段时间又试了一下，pc 端的流畅易用性已经超过 chrome ，尤其是 pdf 阅读体验不可替代；而安卓端更是支持了多个重度使用的插件、包括油猴脚本。并且 edge 的网页翻译比 Firefox 强。\r\n\r\n所以全系切换为 edge 浏览器了，真的好用。chrome 和 Firefox 又落伍了。", "content_rendered": "<p>之前的话主力浏览器一直是 pc 和 mac 端 chrome ，安卓端 Firefox nightly ，ios 端 Safari 。</p>\n<p>之前 edge 用过一段时间又屁滚尿流切换回来了，很多地方的小 bug 不舒服。</p>\n<p>但这段时间又试了一下，pc 端的流畅易用性已经超过 chrome ，尤其是 pdf 阅读体验不可替代；而安卓端更是支持了多个重度使用的插件、包括油猴脚本。并且 edge 的网页翻译比 Firefox 强。</p>\n<p>所以全系切换为 edge 浏览器了，真的好用。chrome 和 Firefox 又落伍了。</p>\n", "last_modified": 1775432986, "replies": 19, "id": 1203752}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/677e/0972/824_large.png?m=1588961795", "name": "router", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/677e/0972/824_normal.png?m=1588961795", "title": "路由器", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/router", "topics": 2147, "footer": "", "header": "数据包流动的乐趣", "title_alternative": "Router", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/677e/0972/824_mini.png?m=1588961795", "stars": 2392, "founder_id": 0, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 824, "parent_node_name": "geek"}, "member": {"id": 560868, "username": "nkwqrwe264556364", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/nkwqrwe264556364", "website": "", "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": "", "tagline": "", "bio": "", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/26b828dbaf0320ba22b77f1ba0faeb31?s=24&d=re